cat <<EOF > README.md
# cordialmente

Monorepo per:
- \`client\`: Next.js frontend (App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind)
- \`backend\`: Strapi headless CMS (TypeScript, SQLite)

## Setup locale

1. \`cd client && npm install\`  
2. \`cd ../backend && npm install\`  
3. Copia \`.env.example\` in \`.env.local\` e definisci le variabili  
4. Avvia:  
   - \`npm run dev\` in \`client\` (Next.js su :3000)  
   - \`npm run develop\` in \`backend\` (Strapi su :1337)
EOF
